        <briefdescription>
<para>XV_vscaler_Initialize - Initialize the <ref refid="struct_x_v__vscaler" kindref="compound">XV_vscaler</ref> instance. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function initializes an <ref refid="struct_x_v__vscaler" kindref="compound">XV_vscaler</ref> instance using the configuration found for the given BaseAddress. It performs a lookup for the configuration structure, validates the instance pointer, and calls the configuration initialization function. If the configuration is not found, it marks the instance as not ready and returns an error code.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to the <ref refid="struct_x_v__vscaler" kindref="compound">XV_vscaler</ref> instance to be initialized. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>BaseAddress</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Base address of the device to look up the configuration.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if initialization is successful.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_DEVICE_NOT_FOUND if the configuration for the given base address is not found. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
